title: The Olive Fairy Book
creator: Andrew Lang
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of The Olive Fairy Book, by Andrew Lang. Andrew Lang’s Olive Fairy Book (1907) was a beautifully produced and illustrated edition of fairy tales that has become a classic. This was one of many other collections of fairy tales, collectively known as Andrew Lang’s Fairy Books. (Summary by Wikipedia) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.
